com.hazelcast.map.impl.query

Class ParallelAccumulationExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.map.impl.query.ParallelAccumulationExecutor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AccumulationExecutor

    public class ParallelAccumulationExecutor
extends Object
implements AccumulationExecutor
    Implementation of the AccumulationExecutor that runs the accumulation in a multi-threaded way. Entries are split into chunks and each chunk is sent as a task to the underlying executor. At the end the result is merged to a single AggregationResult.
